You create a minor illusion designed to wonder and impress. You create one of the effects below within range. If you cast this spell multiple times, you can have up to three of its 1-minute effects active at a time.
- You make a Tiny object that can fit in your hand, such as a coin, disappear and/or reappear.
- You can pull a Tiny beast out of a hat or pocket.

